guide: 7Ideally you'd want Ender Set
7with a Void Sword for this.
7You can buy this for 400 coins
7from the Fish Merchant in the Hub
7Fish in the Hub until you can enter the Backwater Bayou.
7Fish there and lootshare mobs until you unlock
7Fishing Minions. Place as many of them on your island,
7as you can and give them the best fuel and storage
7you have access to and don't forget to collect in time.
7You will get the Rock Pet by mining 2.5k
7Ore Blocks. Keep in mind that Stone doesn't
7count for this. Don't forget to equip the pet ;)
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold and Diamond Armor
7Collect Ender Armor from The End (8 pieces)
7Craft Leaflet, Farm Suit, Mushroom, Cactus
7and Pumpkin Armor.
7Buy Squire, Rosetta's, Celeste, Mercenary and
7Starlight Armor from Rosetta aswell as Angler Armor
7(8 pieces) from the Fishing Merchant,
7Chainmail Armor from the Iron Forger and
7Canopy Armor from Amaury. You should also
7collect the armor from the Foraging Questline.
7Complete a Floor 1 with a score of 230+
7and buy the chest afterwards. If you can't buy
7it on the spot, either save money and buy it
7from Croesus within the next 2 days or do another run.
7You will probably need help with this.
7This needs Combat 15 and a completion
7of the previous floor to enter.
7To efficiently grind this, you should
7get help from Party Finder/Friends.
7Mine Pure Gold in the Dwarven Mines
7with a Fortune 3+ pickaxe.
7You might want to use as many minions
7as you have access to for this.
7Remember to put a compactor in the minions
7when you plan on leaving for a while.
7Don't forget to fuel the minions,
7give them storages and collect them in time.
7Recommended for this is Zombie Slayer.
7This needs 230 xp, so either:
7t1, t2 and 2 t3
7or t1 and 9 t2.
7Don't forget to claim the rewards
7from Maddox.
7Fish in the Hub until you can enter the Backwater Bayou.
7Fish there and lootshare mobs until you unlock
7Fishing Minions. Place as many of them on your island,
7as you can and give them the best fuel and storage
7you have access to and don't forget to collect in time.
7Do commissions and events in The Dwarven Mines,
7claim your daily powder from the Puzzler and
7from giving Fetchur the items he asks for.
7Fetchurs items are all listed in the Wiki.
7Try to do those while a '2x Powder' event is active.
7You might want to use the Royal Reforge on your
7equipment to gain more powder from events.
7You can also fish up and kill Mithril Grubbers
7in the Abandoned Quarry (Fishing 6).
7This unlocks at 2.5k Raw Porkchop Collection
7and requires 40 Enchanted Pork to make.
7You can use Minions for this, just
7remember to give them the best fuel and storage
7you have access to and collect in time.
7Carrots and potatoes from killing
7Zombies in graveyard do count.
7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
7on skyerzz's or prtl's island.
7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End
7and hold it while some Ender Armor and/or Equipment.
7Optimal tool:
7Golden Axe with Efficiency 5
7Reforges: Double-Bit or Lush
7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood
7You could consider getting gear from
7Galatea like Canopy Armor (requires 1.21
7to enter that island)
7Reforge your Void Sword to Sharp
7at the Blacksmith in the Hub or
7enchant any weapon with Critical 5.
7Kill farm animals in the Barn with a Cleaver
7with Cleave 5 and Sharpness 5
7or spiders in Arachne's Burrow
7in the Spider's Den with a Dreadlord Sword.
7You will most likely get this passively.
7Use /be ingame to view your progress once you
7talked to Bramass Beastslayer in The Spiders Den.
7For this you just need to mine blocks,
7complete Mining Commissions and collect
7occasional Commission Milestones.
7Claim your cake buff (visit skyerzz, nightlibra or prtl),
7hold an angler 4+ rod and visit someone with a
7Sea Creature Chance beacon (visit ReyMaratov).
7Ways to obtain:
7Craft (Lapis Lazuli Collection 5),
7a drop from fishing,
7from the Experimentation Table,
7drop from Ender Nodes in the End (11-13%).
7You will most likely be able to complete this
7from doing the Emerald Treasure Goal as there
7is a high chance for a t6 Enchanted Book to be
7in the given Reward Chests.
7Wear armor enchanted with Growth 5
7(Enchanting Level 5), preferably Ender Armor
7while you're in The End.
7Applying Growth 5 costs 50 Levels each.
7If you still struggle, reforge your
7armor to Titanic.
7Use the best fishing rod, bait and armor that you
7have access to and fish in the Spiders Den,
7ideally during rain/thunder and avoid fishing
7IN the hotspots. Recommended is
7Angler Armor (or better) and Carrot Bait.
7You will need Fishing 14 to be able to fish him up.
7Place Fishing Minions and give them the best storage
7(and fuel) you have access to.
7Apply/Use the highest tier of Scavenger
7that you can get your hands on and put it
7on your main weapon. Gifts from the Jerry Island
7can be a way to obtain Scavenger IV books.
7You can also use the weapon drops from dungeon mobs
7as those have guaranteed Scavenger 5.
